title: Joe Budden turned Industry

description:
Wednesday 8/29 - Today on the show Joe Budden pulled up on us, where he discussed what happened with "Everyday Struggle", his new podcast, and right in front of our eyes he was turning "Industry". Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to the 45 year old man Paul who is a serial "Dine and Dasher" and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
